<h2> Edit Your Profile </h2>

<ul class = "errors">
  <% @user.errors.each do |column, message| %>
    <li>
      <strong><%= column.capitalize %></strong> <%= message %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>


<%= form_for @user, url: {action: "update"} do |f| %>
  <p>
    <%= f.label :username %>
    <%= f.text_field :username %>
  </p>
  <p>
    <%= f.label :email %>
    <%= f.text_field :email %>
  </p>
  <%= f.submit "Submit" %>
<% end %>

Also at some time this page will let you update your password with verification,
and will check that your email is valid
